does not require a \code{hess} function. The following parameters apply
only when \code{use_qn = TRUE}.
\describe{
\item{\code{qn_method}}{One of \code{"hybrid"} (default), \code{"sr1"}, \code{"bfgs"}.
\code{"hybrid"} uses state-aware routing between SR1-first and
