recent rho values.}
\item{\code{bfgs_tol}}{Curvature tolerance for the BFGS update
(default \code{1e-10}).}
\item{\code{sr1_skip_tol}}{SR1 skip-test tolerance (default \code{1e-8}).}
\item{\code{sr1_restart_threshold}}{Consecutive SR1 skips before restart
